		"id": "DailyStage_15",
		"name": "1. Daily Challenge tags, stages, and reward chests are reset at 00:00 (UTC+0) every day.
2. Each challenge consumes 10 Stamina and the stage drop rewards are double that of the main stage.
3. Players can claim the corresponding reward chests according to the number of enemies killed every day. Each chest can only be claimed once daily.
4. The more main stages cleared, the more difficult the daily challenge, and the better the drop rewards and chests.
5. Players can challenge up to 3 times daily. The attempts cannot be saved to the next day.
6. The challenge will be counted as successful if 4 challenge chests are claimed in a day. The grand prize will be granted if the player has 5 successful challenges in a week. The grand prize is reset every 7 days."
